title: Faust by Martin Jenkins and Jonathan Holloway - BBC Radio - Seym
description:
FAUST by Martin Jenkins and Jonathan Holloway.

A hilarious reworking of the German legend about a man who sells his soul to the devil, adapted by Martin Jenkins and dramatised by Jonathan Holloway.

Cast:
Mephistopheles ...... Mark Gatiss
Faustus ...... Julian Rhind-Tutt
Wagner ...... Thom Tuck
A Devil ...... Paul Mundell
Martha ...... Pippa Haywood
Gretchen ...... Jasmine Hyde
Valentin ...... Paul Mundell

First broadcast in five parts as the Woman&#039;s Hour Drama in Feb 2008.

65 minutes mixed into one episode.
